('Miniatures','The fine crunchy shell is a perfect taster to enjoy the smooth vanilla, pistachio, raspberry, coconut and praline ice cream.','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Miniatures-Framboise-simple_Dessus-1024x644.png','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Miniature-cover-web-1.png','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-01.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-31.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-13.svg','100% Luxembourg milk;Pleasure break;Practical format','ICECR'),
('Water Sticks','You now don""t need to look elsewhere, Luxlait Ice Cream has developed a range of water-based ice sticks. The sticks are available in several flavours of orange, lemon and coca.','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Watersticks-Mutlipack-Orange_2_HD_-1024x818.png','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Header_Watersticks_2560x800-scaled.jpg','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-13.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-12.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-31.svg','Practical format;Refreshing;Pleasure break','ICECR'),
('Frozen Yoghurt','To produce our Frozen Yoghurt, we use yoghurt instead of cream. Yoghurt contains less fat which makes it healthier. The 200ml pack with its integrated spoon is perfect for taking anywhere. Several flavours: strawberry, peach/passion fruit, salted butterscotch with pecan, vanilla and raspberry. Several flavours are also available in the 1 liter format.','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Frozen-Yogurt-Caramel-1.png','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/AdobeStock_365076608-scaled.jpeg','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-13.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-12.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-31.svg','Practical format;Refreshing;Pleasure break','ICECR'),
