('Dame blanche','With Luxlait Dame Blanche, you will find an essential classic … The refinement of this dessert will awaken your sensitivity. The intensity of the chocolate sauce mixed with the purity of the vanilla ice cream will make you melt with pleasure …','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Boite-dame-blanche_BR-1024x824.png','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Header_Dame-blanche_2560x800-scaled.jpg','https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-13.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-12.svg;https://www.luxlait.lu/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Icon-31.svg','Practical format;Refreshing;Pleasure break','ICECR'),
